Our solutions encompass a wide array of functionality and services, including electronic signatures, biometric authentication and simple-to-complex workflow management. These solutions are available across virtually all enterprise, desktop and mobile environments as a seamlessly integrated platform for both ad-hoc (semi-automated) and fully automated transactions. Our platform can be deployed both on-premise and as a cloud-based service, with the ability to easily transition between deployment models. 
